    "summary": "In this transcript, a Type 1 diabetic user describes symptoms of both hypoglycemia and hyperglycemia, eventually reporting blurry vision and dizziness. The assistant provides medical guidance on how to interpret these symptoms and suggests how to manage insulin corrections based on the user's reported glucose levels and ketone status.",
